    "description": "<u><strong>FarmTD combines the charm of farming with the strategy of tower defense.</strong></u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR TOWERS</h2><i>Many aren't aware, but your farm-animals pack a serious punch!</i><br><br>Get access to a varied range of animal towers to prevent the incoming waves of insects from harming your crops. Use <i>stuns</i> and <i>slows</i> to limit the insects' movement, and don't forget to provide proper illumination at night! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/db892d92977e08dc86d2664f4fc9f161.poster.avif?t=1741343412\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/db892d92977e08dc86d2664f4fc9f161.webm?t=1741343412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/db892d92977e08dc86d2664f4fc9f161.mp4?t=1741343412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW YOUR CROPS</h2><i>Someone has to pay the bills.</i><br><br>While defending yourself from seemingly endless hordes of insects, you have to remember to keep the money flowing! Grow different kinds of plots to not just earn money on your investment, but also win favor with the townsfolk.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/aeb39d9990df70a5cb8664f17ce192c0.avif?t=1741343412\" width=616 height=290 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY YOUR WAY</h2><i>We're all individuals!</i><br><br>Are you someone who plays for lategame? Power through the early? Win the favor of the town? Play with permanent upgrades? <br>Play whatever playstyle you prefer in one of the four difficulty settings. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/ecfa7d8004fe86b4c4e6c7268957cb0a.poster.avif?t=1741343412\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/ecfa7d8004fe86b4c4e6c7268957cb0a.webm?t=1741343412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/ecfa7d8004fe86b4c4e6c7268957cb0a.mp4?t=1741343412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JOIN THE DISCORD</h2><i>Sometimes a single-player game needs a player 2.</i><br><br>Do you want to share you insight, tactics, passion, or suggestions with other farmers? <br>Press the Discord Link on the right  -&gt; <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081300/extras/ffc141170c5448d08e7318520404872b.avif?t=1741343412\" width=616 height=347 /></span>",
